    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your connection to the hungering undead shapes your magic.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Class Skill:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/stealth\">Stealth</a>.</p>\n<div>\n<h4><span id=\"Bonus_Spells\"><a name=\"TOC-Bonus-Spells\"></a><strong>Bonus Spells: </strong></span></h4>\n<ul>\n<li><span id=\"Bonus_Spells\">@Compendium[pf1.spells.mczdgwo3xl8c6e26]{Ray Of Enfeeblement}</span>&nbsp;(3rd),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.23pgt0f34obki95q]{Feast Of Ashes}&nbsp;(5th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.3efy1ico48ccrzni]{Vampiric Touch}&nbsp;(7th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.be88e90guqbi1q1z]{Fear}&nbsp;(9th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.y2byo50vj2hrltl4]{Hungry Earth}&nbsp;(11th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.ukuyfbufbglbzfco]{Move Earth}&nbsp;(13th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.wkp8u7xl1dgpk362]{Control Undead}&nbsp;(15th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.flrn1xmm2wfrxbkf]{Unholy Aura}&nbsp;(17th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.wplgawb6aznjx7se]{Wail of the Banshee}&nbsp;(19th).</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><span id=\"Bonus_Feats\"><a name=\"TOC-Bonus-Feats\"></a><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong> </span></h4>\n<ul>\n<li><span id=\"Bonus_Feats\">@Compendium[pf1.feats.QvlxYVVsBDlykPKe]{Arcane Strike<strong>}</strong></span>,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.u7rGDZUL296QIuA0]{Combat Casting},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.FUW5mIXHNBBIQ1Sq]{Power Attack},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;[religion]),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.V2zY7BltkpSXwejy]{Spell Focus}(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Necromancy\">necromancy</a>),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.8snLqsJN4LLL00Nq]{Toughness},</li>\n<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/monster-feats/warren-digger\">Warren Digger</a>*,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.vWiTqHC4Y3Xn1Pme]{Weapon Finesse}.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><span id=\"Bloodline_Arcana\"><a name=\"TOC-Bloodline-Arcana\"></a><strong>Bloodline Arcana:&nbsp;</strong></span>Whenever you cast a spell of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Necromancy\">necromancy</a>&nbsp;school that deals hit point damage, you are healed of 1 hit point per spell level.</h4>\n</div>",
